    "   In high SNR, the slope of the probability of error curve is determined by **diversity gain** $d$.\n",
    "  - In a $3 \\times 1$ MISO system, $d = N_t = 3$.  \n",
    "   Therefore, the slope is **$-3$** when plotted in log-log scale.\n",
