    "$R = 6 \\times 2 = 12 \\, \\text{bpcu}$\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Slope:**  \n",
    "   The slope of the probability of error in high SNR is still given by the diversity gain $d = 3$.  \n",
    "   Thus, the slope remains **$-3$**."
