    "\n",
    "$X_1 = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & -1 \\\\ 1 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}, X_2 = \\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 1 \\\\ -1 & 1 \\end{bmatrix}, X_3 = \\begin{bmatrix} -1 & -1 \\\\ 1 & -1 \\end{bmatrix}$ and $X_4 = \\begin{bmatrix} -1 & 1 \\\\ -1 & -1 \\end{bmatrix}$\n",
